{
  "stem": "7414.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and she decided that as I am so young and everything is all right, I will give birth at home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After one day, she saw that something is wrong.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she rang the women's hospital, and they accepted me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a very rare thing because the hospitals were full, and you could not-- but the matron of the hospital was a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no, school friend of Aunt Paula.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So she found for me room there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I will not tell you the whole story because it is too long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was in labor two days and two nights.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Nothing happens.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was absolutely-- everybody was panicked-- panicking, and that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "On the night of the second-- second night, it started to get everything out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The baby is coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By then, everybody was around me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The head doctor and all the doctors and all the nurses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had nothing else to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was standing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The difficult birth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I needed the last push when suddenly I saw the door open, and the nurse is coming in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She had one look at me, and she tells, what she's doing here, she's Jewish?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And everything stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could not push.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could not-- I just felt faint.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were all standing around me, and nobody understood what happened with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then-- today, after 50-odd years, when I think about this moment, I can't understand why the others did-- did not react when she told it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did not hear?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I heard it on my bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then I-- I don't know if it was my imagination, or my-- the-- the fear or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I can see her and hear her voice even now.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
